Class PointMemberWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gvsig.gpe.prov.gml.writer.v2.geometries.GeometryWriter
      • org.gvsig.gpe.prov.gml.writer.v2.geometries.PointMemberWriter

  • public class PointMemberWriter
extends GeometryWriter
    It writes a gml:pointMemberType object. Example: 

     
 <pointMember>
 <Point gid="P6776">
 <coord><X>50.0</X><Y>50.0</Y></coord>
 </Point>
 </pointMember>
